---
// src/components/SidecarMode.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-[#0B1120] text-white relative overflow-hidden border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] bg-center [mask-image:linear-gradient(180deg,white,rgba(255,255,255,0))] opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[1000px] h-[400px] bg-blue-500/20 rounded-[100%] blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-blue-400 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4">
        The Zero-Risk Protocol
    </h2>
    <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight text-white">
        Got a website, but no customers? <br>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300">It doesn't matter.</span>
    </h3>
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        No need to worry, your website can run like usual. 
        <strong>Stegg is the antidote.</strong> We just build a "powerful marketing engine" right next door. Zero downtime. Zero risk.
    </p>
</div>

        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24">
            
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 hidden md:flex justify-center items-center">
                <div class="bg-[#0B1120] p-2 rounded-full border border-slate-700">
                    <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-500"></i>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-8 relative">
                
                <div class="bg-[#0f172a] rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-800 relative group">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-700">
                            <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-400"></i>
                        </div>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-900 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 border border-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            Do Not Touch
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Your Main Website</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8">The "Main Clinic"</p>

                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50">
                            <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Access Needed</span>
                            <span class="text-slate-300 font-mono text-sm">None</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-800/50">
                            <span class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Risk Level</span>
                            <span class="text-green-500 font-mono text-sm">0% (Safe)</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-blue-900/10 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-blue-500/30 relative overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/20 blur-[60px] pointer-events-none"></div>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8 relative z-10">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border border-blue-400 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/50">
                            <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-6 h-6 text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold text-blue-300 border border-blue-500/30 uppercase tracking-wider animate-pulse">
                            Active Zone
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 relative z-10">The Marketing Wing</h3>
                    <p class="text-blue-300 text-sm mb-8 relative z-10">The Stegg Engine</p>

                    <div class="space-y-3 relative z-10">
                         <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-blue-950/40 rounded-lg border border-blue-500/20">
                            <span class="text-blue-200 text-sm">Role</span>
                            <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm">Catch Traffic</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-blue-950/40 rounded-lg border border-blue-500/20">
                            <span class="text-blue-200 text-sm">Output</span>
                            <span class="text-white font-mono text-sm">WhatsApp Leads</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            
            <div class="group bg-slate-800/50 hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors border border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-500/50 rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default">
                <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-slate-700 rounded-xl group-hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">
                        <span class="font-bold text-white text-lg">01</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 group-hover:text-blue-400">Best for Authority</span>
                </div>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The "Extension" Strategy</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 min-h-[40px]">
                    We build on your own land. We connect a new "wing" to your existing domain (e.g. <em>locations.yourclinic.com</em>).
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-black/40 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 p-3">
                    <div class="flex gap-1.5 mb-2 opacity-50">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono text-slate-300 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-3 h-3 text-green-500"></i>
                        <span class="text-blue-400">locations</span><span class="text-slate-500">.</span>yourclinic.com
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group bg-slate-800/50 hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors border border-slate-700 hover:border-cyan-500/50 rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default">
                 <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
                    <div class="p-3 bg-slate-700 rounded-xl group-hover:bg-cyan-600 transition-colors">
                        <span class="font-bold text-white text-lg">02</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 group-hover:text-cyan-400">Best for Speed</span>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The "Billboard" Strategy</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-6 min-h-[40px]">
                    Lost your password? No problem. We simply buy a new plot of land nearby (e.g. <em>yourclinic-growth.com</em>) and point it to you.
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-black/40 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 p-3">
                    <div class="flex gap-1.5 mb-2 opacity-50">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono text-slate-300 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-3 h-3 text-green-500"></i>
                        yourclinic<span class="text-cyan-400">-growth</span>.com
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500"></i>
                Both options include 100% Managed Hosting & Security by Stegg.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>